\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14957223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14813229\charrsid9520696 Did you always have the same place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11013156 HH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14813229\charrsid9520696 Yes, yes, yes, we always had the same place.
