\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14957223 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14813229\charrsid9520696 That must have taken a lot of saving up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11013156 HH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14813229\charrsid9520696 Take - aye, took - took - quite a bit of saving up, mm hm.
